    "Retrospective dataset with 2128 cycles of 1731 women in a single center.",
    "88.8% were GnRH-ant (fixed) cycles.",
    "An hCG trigger was used.",
    "Input variables: age, AFC, follicle count by size on each scan.",
    "Average improvement of 2PNs (primary outcome), and usable blastocysts vs. a clinician's decision."
